name: Get me home (PseudoGamer01)
description:
Simple man, wants to go home, which is across the river, we just need to help him collect as many as coin possible.

Another Super casual game for you guys.
Nothing fancy, just simple game to kill time.

Fully cartoonish, Colorful game for all age group.

This game depends onto you judgement and nothin at all.

Lets see how gets the most.
